      <h2 id="special-thoughts-on-healing-after-losing-a-pet">Special Thoughts on Healing After Losing a Pet</h2>
      <p></p>
<p>The journey of healing after pet loss is unique to each individual.  Allowing oneself time to grieve, remembering the happy times, and seeking support are essential parts of this process.  Remember that your friend's grief is valid and significant, and that healing takes time.</p>
